---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

const title = 'Furniture Fulfillment | Specialized Packaging, Assembly, 48-Hour Delivery, 100% Insurance | MTP';
const description = 'Specialized fulfillment for large furniture, couches, beds, tables, cabinets. Wooden frames, foam protection, specialist assembly on-site, 48-hour delivery, 100% insurance coverage across Ukraine.';
const ogImage = 'https://profm.ua/images/fulfillment-furniture.jpg';

const schema = {
  '@context': 'https://schema.org',
  '@type': 'Service',
  name: title,
  description: description,
  provider: {
    '@type': 'Organization',
    name: 'MTP Group',
    url: 'https://profm.ua/en/'
  },
  areaServed: {
    '@type': 'Country',
    name: 'UA'
  },
  priceRange: '₴200-₴500'
};
---

<Base title={title} description={description} ogImage={ogImage} lang="en">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
        Furniture Fulfillment<br />Specialized Handling, Assembly, 48-Hour Delivery
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-95 leading-relaxed">
        Couches, beds, cabinets, tables. Custom packaging with wooden frames and foam, specialized transport, professional assembly on-site, 100% insurance, 48-hour guaranteed delivery.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Start Furniture Fulfillment
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Furniture Requires Specialized Fulfillment</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">📦 Large Size &amp; Weight</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">150kg couches don't fit standard boxes. Requires pallets, wooden frames, polyethylene wrap, air cushioning. Wrong packaging = scratched couch = full loss and refund.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💰 High-Value Goods</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">A chair worth 8000 UAH damaged in transit = 8000 UAH loss + negative review. Furniture damage is catastrophic. Requires maximum protection and 100% insurance coverage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🚚 Complex Logistics</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Furniture requires 5-20 ton vehicles, trained unloading crews, careful placement in homes. Standard courier cannot handle furniture. Need specialists with equipment and insurance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔧 Assembly &amp; Service</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Some furniture requires assembly at customer location. Customers expect delivery plus professional setup. Need trained technicians, tools, quality assurance on-site.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

\1  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">How MTP Group Handles Furniture Orders</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          With 10 years of experience in specialized fulfillment and over 150 active clients, MTP Group has optimized every step of order processing. Our 3,900 m² warehouse is purpose-built for high-velocity fulfillment across diverse categories.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">The Fulfillment Challenge</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Furniture fulfillment demands specialized logistics: orders are high-volume, often require assembly or disassembly, and demand white-glove delivery. A single order might include multiple pieces.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          MTP Group's approach: Our 5–20 ton vehicles and trained drivers ensure damage-free delivery. Furniture is wrapped, strapped, and protected. We can coordinate installation or assembly. Processing includes dimensional verification, weight confirmation, and photo documentation.
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why Retailers Choose MTP</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Furniture orders average ₴2,000–5,000. Damage or delivery issues result in ₴500–2,000 refund costs. Our specialized transport and 99.7% accuracy protect high-value orders.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          MTP Group has processed <strong>8,000+ furniture orders processed, 25+ furniture retailers served</strong>. Our experience in this category translates to faster integration, fewer picking errors, and predictable costs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

   Furniture Fulfillment Services</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Specialized Protective Packaging</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Wooden frames, foam corners, polyethylene wrap, air cushioning. Protection from scratches, dents, water damage. Custom packaging per furniture type. Maximum durability in transit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Specialized Transport &amp; Delivery</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">5-20 ton vehicles. Trained unloading crews. GPS tracking throughout journey. Photo documentation before delivery, after unloading, placement in home. Damage assessment on-site.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ Professional Assembly &amp; Service</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Chairs, beds, tables assembled by specialist team. All bolts tightened, stability checked. Customer shown how to maintain furniture. Tools and materials included. Quality guarantee on assembly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-2">✓ 100% Damage Insurance &amp; Instant Reimbursement</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Couch arrives damaged = 100% refund. No waiting for approval. Instant compensation on-site. Customer satisfaction guaranteed. Full peace of mind for high-value orders.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Pricing for Furniture</h2>
      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border border-gray-200 mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-4">Fulfillment, Delivery &amp; Assembly</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Picking &amp; preparation per order</span>
            <span class="font-bold">50–100 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Specialized protective packaging</span>
            <span class="font-bold">20–50 UAH per item</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Specialized delivery (up to 50 km)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">200–500 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Assembly service per piece</span>
            <span class="font-bold">100–300 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>Storage (per pallet/month)</span>
            <span class="font-bold">400–500 UAH</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex justify-between">
            <span>100% insurance coverage</span>
            <span class="font-bold">Included</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
        <h3 class="font-bold mb-3">Example: Furniture Store (50 orders/month)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Picking &amp; prep: 50 × 75 = 3,750 UAH<br/>
          Protective packaging: 50 × 30 = 1,500 UAH<br/>
          Specialized delivery: 50 × 350 = 17,500 UAH<br/>
          Assembly service: 50 × 200 = 10,000 UAH<br/>
          Storage (5 pallets): 5 × 450 = 2,250 UAH/month<br/>
          <strong class="text-lg">TOTAL: 35,000 UAH/month = 700 UAH per order</strong><br/>
          <span class="text-sm text-gray-600">Includes: specialized packaging, 48-hour delivery, professional assembly, 100% insurance</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Quality Guarantees</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">&lt;0.5%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Damage Rate</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Specialized packaging &amp; trained delivery crews</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">48h</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Delivery Guarantee</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Fast transport with professional setup on-site</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center bg-white p-6 rounded border border-green-200">
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-2">100%</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold">Insurance Coverage</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-2">Full reimbursement for any damage or loss</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


  <section class="py-16 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Why Fulfillment Speed & Accuracy Matter for Your Business</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">⏱️ Speed = Competitive Advantage</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">E-commerce customers expect 24-48 hour delivery. Slow fulfillment leads to lost orders and negative reviews. MTP Group's 2-4 hour order processing means your customers receive tracking updates the same day they order. This builds trust and encourages repeat purchases. Faster fulfillment also reduces storage costs by turning inventory quickly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">✅ Accuracy = Customer Retention</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Wrong item? The customer will return it, costing you both labor and shipping. Wrong quantity? Dispute and potential chargeback. Our 99.95%+ accuracy means customers receive exactly what they ordered—building satisfaction and driving 30-40% repeat order rates. Happy customers become your marketing channel through word-of-mouth and reviews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">💰 Margins Are Everything</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Fulfillment is often 10-20% of your total order cost. Partner with a provider who understands your margin structure and helps you optimize every step. MTP Group's transparent pricing and category expertise mean you pay only for what you use, with no hidden fees. Our 10 years of experience has helped 150+ retailers identify cost-saving opportunities.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded border-l-4 border-red-600">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold mb-3">🔄 Scaling Without Stress</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Black Friday. Holiday season. New product launch. These peak periods either make or break your year. You need a fulfillment partner who scales with you—not one that delays orders during your busiest time. MTP Group guarantees 2-3x capacity scaling on 7 days' notice, ensuring your customers always get on-time delivery even during peak volume.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-500 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Ready to Streamline Your Furniture Fulfillment?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">
        Specialized packaging, professional assembly, 48-hour delivery, 100% insurance. Start today.
      </p>
      <a href="#contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 px-8 py-4 rounded font-bold text-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
        Request a Quote
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)}></script>
</Base>
